BEGIN:VTODO
UID:TODO-32BF6118-C2E4-459D-B474-F96A8F632B7B
DTSTAMP:20260417T063941Z
SUMMARY:Aniketh Mikkilineni [@axm]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-04-14 Tue 12:00-15:00>\n1. Independent Study\n   1. Wait 
 until Friday\, if nothing proceed with Biochem route.\n2. Re-read Sakai200
 0\n   1. ☑ Available premixed lipids like Presome?  Doesn't seem so.\n   2
 . ☒ What is P50?  How to measure it?\n   3. ☑ Why are PLP and HCys co-enca
 psulated?\n3. ☑ Differences in Hb (oxyHb\, deoxyHb)\, Mb\, LegH?\n4. Refer
  to plan sketch about by Coviello\n5. ☑ Borrow DPPC and DOPC in CHCl3 from
  Santore\, 25 mg/mL and 10\n   mg/mL.  Maria said to backfill with nitroge
 n before storing.\n6. ☒ Borrow Chol and possibly HCys from Emrick (via Tap
 iwa).\n7. ☑ Myoglobin? Expensive (about $200 per 1g\, cf. Hb which is $37 
 per\n   5g)\n8. ☑ Contact Dong Wang.
CATEGORIES:@axm,BRG
SEQUENCE:1
PRIORITY:5
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
END:VTODO
